fltk: FLTK - The Fast Light Tool Kit ("FLTK", pronounced "fulltick")
fltk:
fltk: FLTK is a cross-platform C++ GUI toolkit for for UNIX(r)/Linux(r)
fltk: (X11), Microsoft(r) Windows(r), and MacOS(r) X. FLTK provides modern
fltk: GUI functionality without the bloat and supports 3D graphics via
fltk: OpenGL(r) and its built-in GLUT emulation.  FLTK also includes
fltk: an excellent UI builder called FLUID that can be used to create
fltk: applications in minutes.
fltk: 
fltk: FLTK is provided under the terms of the GNU Library Public License,
fltk: Version 2 with exceptions that allow for static linking.
